body_html:
@tfboyd I'm unassigning myself because I know very little about the RPC layer and know nothing about VERBs. I don't think this is a bug with tf_cnn_benchmarks, because #11416 also has the same issue with a different model.

@suiyuan2009 I don't think tensorflow/benchmarks#38 is the same issue, since this issue only occurs with verbs, and it occurs with another model with verbs. I'll take a look at tensorflow/benchmarks#38 though.
